New Records: Rohit Sharma broke AB de Villiers's 8-year-old record for most sixes in a calendar year in ODIs with 59 sixes in 2023
Key Match Events: Rohit Sharma and Shubman Gill added 90 runs in the first 10 overs
Rohit Sharma hit his 59th six of 2023 in the 7th over
Miscellaneous Highlights: India raced to 73 for 0 in just 8 overs
The crowd was treated to some ruthless, high-quality hitting from the two Indian openers
